<section class="method" id="report-request-comprehensive">
  <div class="method-copy">
    <h2>Comprehensive Example</h2>
    <p>The report request has many optional data elements. Additionally, some elements are conditional, meaning that your request must include at least one element out of a set of possible elements.</p>
    <p>This example includes all required elements and most of the optional elements. For conditional elements, this example includes all possible options. There are notes where conditional elements are present.</p>
    <p>Note: Some optional elements have been ommitted because they are not useful for the vast majority of users. For more information on these rarely used elements, consult the <%= link_to 'report request XML schema', './data/report_request_schema.xsd' %>.</p>
  </div><!-- .method-copy -->

  <div class="method-code">
    <div class="method-example method-example-definition">
      <h3>Definition</h3>
<% code('shell') do %>
POST https://gateway-prep.pmp.appriss.com/narxreport/{REPORT_ID}.html
<% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="method-example method-example-request">
      <h3>Example Request</h3>
<% code('shell') do %>
curl https://gateway-prep.pmp.appriss.com/narx/request/simple \
  -u username:password \
  -H "Content-Type: application/xml" \
  -H "Accept: application/xml" \
  -d @report_request_comprehensive.xml
<% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="method-example method-example-request-data">
      <h3>Example Request Data</h3>
      <p class="filename">report_request_comprehensive.xml</p>
      <span class="download">
        <a href="./data/report_request_comprehensive.xml" download>download</a>
      </span>
<% code('xml') do %>
  <% File.open("#{root}/source/data/report_request_comprehensive.xml", 'rb').read %>
<% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="method-example method-example-request-data">
      <h3>Example Response</h3>
<% code('xml') do %>
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<NarxReportResponse xmlns="http://xml.appriss.com/gateway">
  <NarxReportRequestId>2332</NarxReportRequestId>
  <ReportLink>https://gateway-prep.pmp.appriss.com/narxreportlink/693a2297-0a55-4980-b525-574f42d6b46b</ReportLink>
</NarxReportResponse>
<% end %>
    </div>
  </div><!-- .method-code -->
</section>
